Since when do you ever count on a charmed mob casting a spell? And when a mob that you charm finishes a spell cast on you that it started before you charmed it, it doesn't work. I have seen that message many times. 
<br />

<br />
"A Ranting Holgresh tries to cast a spell on you, but you are protected."
<br />

<br />
As far as a heal for another mob, I can't tell you what happens, which says to me that it is sooooo rare as to not worry about it, as I use charm quite a bit. But I bet that heal doesn't work, based on the message above- which seems to indicate that now that you and your pet are both 'on the same side' so to speak, it would follow the same rules as if a PC healed a NPC mob- i.e. it fails silently.
<br />

