It's not about security.  It's about time and knowledge.  Assuming that exploiters know all the exploits in the game is also a fallacy.  Period.  Getting a small amount of people to know so that they can go "SoE, you're slacking here", that's one thing.  Letting every single damn person on every server know, that's asking for a sloppy patch.</td>	</tr></table><span class="postbody">Again, I do not advocate public disclosure of bugs that aren't fixed yet.  
